content.title: Cur-my-ner.
content.howToUseTooltip:
Ta cuid jeh'n markaghey shoh ry-gheddyn son obbraghyn, myr click, llieeney text, etc.

Ta'n aght t'ayn ry-gheddyn ayns y duillag app. Mannagh vel oo ry-gheddyn duplicate, cur-my-ner roghnin elley dy ghra uniqueness.

Ta fockle red cur fys dy vel y ghraih attribute er ny yannoo reesht, ta fockle glass soilshaghey magh dy vel y ghraih attribute ymmyrchagh ayns y rannagh paginagh nish, as ta fockle dooghyssagh soilshaghey magh nagh vel co-chosney ry-gheddyn.
content.otherNodesSummary: Nodyn elley ayns y raad shoh
content.moreNodes: Ta shen ny ta er ny h-earroo.
